#: kb/models.py:1176
msgid ""
"How long an administrator may stay inactive inside Django Admin after "
"completing the extra admin MFA check. Default is 600 seconds (10 minutes). "
"Minimum enforced by code is 60 seconds; maximum enforced by code is 86400 "
"seconds."
msgstr ""
"管理员完成额外管理员 MFA 检查后，可在 Django 管理后台保持空闲的最长时间。默认值为 600 秒（10 分钟）。代码强制的最小值为 60 "
"秒，最大值为 86400 秒。"

#: kb/admin.py:253 kb/models.py:1101
msgid ""
"How long deleted published articles remain recoverable in My Profile → Admin"
" tools → Deletion queue before permanent deletion. Default is 7 days. Set to"
" 0 to permanently delete published articles immediately after MFA "
"confirmation."
msgstr ""
"已删除的已发布文章在“我的个人资料 → 管理工具 → 删除队列”中，在永久删除前可恢复的时长。默认值为 7 天。设为 0 则在 MFA "
"确认后立即永久删除已发布文章。"

#: kb/admin.py:260
msgid ""
"How long failed-login/MFA escalation history is remembered without a "
"successful login. Successful verification clears it immediately. Default is "
"604800 seconds (7 days)."
msgstr "在未成功登录的情况下，失败登录/MFA 升级历史会保留多久。成功验证会立即清除它。默认值为 604800 秒（7 天）。"

#: kb/models.py:1167
msgid ""
"How long failed-login/MFA lockout history is remembered if the user never "
"signs in successfully. Successful password/MFA verification resets the "
"relevant lockout history immediately. Default is 604800 seconds (7 days)."
msgstr ""
"如果用户始终未成功登录，失败登录/MFA 锁定历史会保留多久。成功完成密码/MFA 验证会立即重置相关锁定历史。默认值为 604800 秒（7 天）。"

#: kb/admin.py:263 kb/models.py:1228
msgid "How long the login/MFA check is blocked after this stage triggers."
msgstr "此阶段触发后，登录/MFA 检查被锁定的时长。"

#: kb/admin.py:264 kb/models.py:1233
